1. yum update 升级所有软件包

2. 安装epel软件源,用于安装nginx, mysql-server
rpm -Uvh http://mirrors.sohu.com/fedora-epel/6/x86_64/epel-release-6-8.noarch.rpm
yum install nginx mysql-server

3. 配置remi repository ， 安装php-fpm
rpm -Uvh http://mirrors.mediatemple.net/remi/enterprise/remi-release-6.rpm
yum install php-mysql php-mcrypt php-fpm php-mbstring

4. 配置自启动 php,nginx,mysql-server
chkconfig nginx on
chkconfig php-fpm on
chkconfig mysqld on

5. 启动nginx, php-fpm mysql-server
service nginx start
service php-fpm start
service mysqld start

6. 确认进程是否有正常启动
ps aux | grep nginx
ps aux | grep php-fpm
ps aux | grep mysqld

7. 禁用iptables，开发环境不开防火墙
service iptables stop
chkconfig iptables off

8. php fpm默认监听在9000端口，配置nginx转发所有php的请求给php-fpm解析执行
mkdir /var/www/default  -p

<?php
phpinfo();

nginx的配置文件/etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf
server {
    listen       80 default_server;
    server_name  _;
    root /var/www/default;
    index index.html index.php;

    location ~ \.php$ {
        fastcgi_pass   127.0.0.1:9000;
        fastcgi_index  index.php;
        fastcgi_param  SCRIPT_FILENAME  $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;
        include        fastcgi_params;
    }
}

9. 测试nginx配置是否正常，然后重启nginx服务
service nginx configtest
service nginx restart

